						<div class="postbody">Changelog:<br />0.81<br />Added option &quot;TV Aspect Ratio&quot; in the video settings that simulates the screen format of the old televisions (4:3).<br />Added option &quot;Interpolation&quot; which enables, regardless of the type of filter used, the bilinear interpolation of the image.<br />Set to &quot;1&quot; the default value for the delay of the turbo buttons.<br />Fixed a memory leak in version D3D9.</div>

